General.Name: Asiana IDT Inc
General.Description: Asiana IDT, Inc. provides ICT services in South Korea. The company provides consulting, system development, and IT outsourcing services, as well as operation and maintenance services. It serves airline, construction, airport, finance, transportation, and manufacturing sectors. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Seoul, South Korea. Asiana IDT, Inc. is a subsidiary of Asiana Airlines, Inc.
